{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/cloud service/docker-기본-개념/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Moomi's develog","author":"Moomi","siteUrl":"https://moomi98.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"/Moomi98"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"Moomi98"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c0c7e0f4-736f-53d2-a5af-90e53670a3bc","excerpt":"🐋 Docker란? Docker는 컨테이너 기반의 오픈소스 가상화 플랫폼이다. 기존에는 주로 OS 가상화를 통해 호스트 OS 위에 게스트 OS를 돌리는 방식으로 작동했다. 이러한 방식은 OS를 자유롭게 사용할 수 있지만, 무겁고 느리다는 단점이 있다. 이를 해결하기 위해 프로세스 단위로 가상화를 하는 방법이 등장했고, 이 중 리눅스에서 지원하는 리눅스 컨테이너를 활용한 가상화 플랫폼이 Docker이다. 🪄 실행 방법 1. repository 인덱스 갱신하기 2. Docker…","html":"<h2 id=\"-docker란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-docker%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\" docker란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>🐋 Docker란?</h2>\n<p>Docker는 컨테이너 기반의 오픈소스 가상화 플랫폼이다.</p>\n<p>기존에는 주로 OS 가상화를 통해 호스트 OS 위에 게스트 OS를 돌리는 방식으로 작동했다.</p>\n<p>이러한 방식은 OS를 자유롭게 사용할 수 있지만, 무겁고 느리다는 단점이 있다.</p>\n<p>이를 해결하기 위해 프로세스 단위로 가상화를 하는 방법이 등장했고, 이 중 리눅스에서 지원하는 <strong>리눅스 컨테이너</strong>를 활용한 가상화 플랫폼이 Docker이다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"-실행-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\" 실행 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>🪄 실행 방법</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-repository-인덱스-갱신하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-repository-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4-%EA%B0%B1%EC%8B%A0%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"1 repository 인덱스 갱신하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. repository 인덱스 갱신하기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> update</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"2-docker-다운을-위해-필요한-패키지-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-docker-%EB%8B%A4%EC%9A%B4%EC%9D%84-%EC%9C%84%ED%95%B4-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%ED%95%9C-%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"2 docker 다운을 위해 필요한 패키지 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Docker 다운을 위해 필요한 패키지 설치</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> apt-transport-https\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> ca-certificates\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token function\">curl</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> software-properties-common</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"3-curl-명령어로-docker-다운로드\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-curl-%EB%AA%85%EB%A0%B9%EC%96%B4%EB%A1%9C-docker-%EB%8B%A4%EC%9A%B4%EB%A1%9C%EB%93%9C\" aria-label=\"3 curl 명령어로 docker 다운로드 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. curl 명령어로 Docker 다운로드</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">curl</span> -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu/gpg <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> apt-key <span class=\"token function\">add</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"4-repository에-경로-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-repository%EC%97%90-%EA%B2%BD%EB%A1%9C-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"4 repository에 경로 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. repository에 경로 추가</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> add-apt-repository <span class=\"token string\">\"deb [arch=amd64] https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu bionic stable\"</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> update</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"5-docker-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-docker-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"5 docker 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. Docker 설치</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">apt-cache</span> policy docker-ce\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> docker-ce</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"6-이미지-다운로드\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6-%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80-%EB%8B%A4%EC%9A%B4%EB%A1%9C%EB%93%9C\" aria-label=\"6 이미지 다운로드 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6. 이미지 다운로드</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">docker</span> pull hello-world\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">docker</span> images\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">docker</span> run hello-world\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">docker</span> <span class=\"token function\">ps</span> -a\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">docker</span> <span class=\"token function\">rm</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>containerID<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">docker</span> images</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Docker 기본 개념","date":"May 30, 2022"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/cloud service/docker-기본-개념/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/web/웹-스토리지와-쿠키/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"웹 스토리지와 쿠키"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/React/re-rendering이-되는-상황들/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Re-rendering이 되는 상황들"}}}